Package entity

Class Project

java.lang.Object
entity.Project
public class Project extends Object
Represents a BTO project that contains flat types, pricing, officer assignment, availability status, and application time window.

  • Method Details

    • decrementFlat

      public void decrementFlat(String flatType)
      Decrements the count of available flats of the specified type by 1, if there is at least one available. If no such flat is available, an error message is printed to the standard error stream.
      Parameters:
      flatType - the type of flat to decrement availability for (e.g., "2-Room", "3-Room")
